title.en: Kazoku ni Yakudatazu to Iware Tsuzuketa Watashi ga, Mashou no Koushaku Kishi-sama no Saiai ni naru made
Tensei shitara Saiai no Kazoku ni Mouichido Deaemashita ~Afureru Ai wo Kono Hitosara ni Nosete~
Watashi no Konyakusha-sama no Dokuzetsu ga Sugiru ~Minna ni Shio Taiou no Hazu ga Watashi wa Dekiai Sareteimasu~
Gimai ga Seijo dakara to Konyakuhaki Saremashita ga, Watashi wa Yousei no Itoshigo desu
Iekara Nigedashitai Watashi ga, Ukkari Akogare no Daimahoutsukai-sama wo Katteshimattara
Konyaku Haki no Tsugi wa Gisou Konyaku. Sate, Sono Ji wa...
Ochikobore Reijou wa, Koushaku Kakka kara no Dekiai ni Kizukanai ~Konyakusha ni Shimeisareta no wa Saishoku Kenbi no Ane de wa Naku, Watashi deshita~
Rikon Yotei no Keiyaku Konna no ni, Reikoku Koushaku-sama ni Shuuchakusareteimasu
Higeki no Heroine Buru Imouto no Sei de Konyaku Hakishita no desu ga, Naze ka Seigikan no Tsuyoi Outaishi ni Karamareru you ni narimashita
Itsuwari no Seijo wa Ryuukoku no Mahoutsukai ni narimashita
Konyaku Haki Sareta Kaedama Reijou, Hatsukoi no Toshiue Ouji ni Dekiai Sareru
Imouto ni Konyakusha wo Toraretara, Juuna Ouji ni Kyuukon saremashita
Ochibure Saijo no Koufuku Heika ni Suterareta no de, Saiai no Hito wo Sukui ni ikimasu
10-nenkan Karada wo Nottorare Akujo ni natte Ita Watashi ni, Nidoto Kao wo Miseru na to Konyaku Haki shite Kita Kishi-sama ga Kyou mo Sugatte kuru
Danna-sama ga Chicchai Mofumofu ni narimashita ~Watashi wo Akujo da to Gokai shiteita no ni, Subete Gibo no Uso da to Kizuita you desu~
Shukujo no Kagami Yamemashita. Toki wo Gyakkou shita Koushaku Reijou wa, Wagamama na Imouto ni Furimawasarenai you Seikaku Waruku Ikinobimasu!
Senjou no Seijo ~Imouto no Kawari ni Koushaku Kishi ni Totsugu Koto ni narimashita ga, Ima wa Shiawase desu~
